metadata.symbol: Collectible digital cards celebrating our world!
metadata.description:
This Guba (UbaGuba collectible cards) celebrates 1 January 1999, when the European Monetary Union adopted the Euro as its single currency.

  • 10 Bronze Gubas exist of this date.
  • 4 Silver Gubas exist of this date.
  • 1 Gold Guba exists of this date.
metadata.title: January 1 - Bronze Guba - The Euro
metadata.subtitle: 01/JAN/1999: the European Monetary Union adopted the Euro as its single currency
metadata.name: JAN01 - Bronze Guba - The Euro
